title: [Fethayl Bog, Caretaker's Hovel]
description: A gnarled, dead oak tree looms to the east, overshadowing a small dilapidated hovel.  Sitting lopsided amongst the marshy swamp, the hovel is overgrown with moss clinging tightly to the walls.  A small, marble bench sits on a lone patch of dry ground, just in front of the hovel.
